gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 120, Raptors 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Raptors, 120-105. Stephen Curry led the way for the Warriors with 25 points (7-15 3PT FG), six rebounds and six assists, while Jonathan Kuminga added 24 points and six rebounds in the victory. RJ Barrett notched 23 points and four assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Warriors win their third straight game as they improve to 32-27 on the season, while the Raptors fall to 22-38.
